</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A24157E21977FFB06A8BA7E07131F835" box="[189,285,1927,1953]" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D081977FFB06B1DA7EF71FDF835" authorityName="Hippa, van Steenis &amp; Mutin" authorityYear="2015" box="[299,465,1927,1954]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nasuta" subGenus="Asiosphegina">
<emphasis id="B972EA991977FFB06B1DA7EF71FDF835" box="[299,465,1927,1954]" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">S. (A.) nasuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D081977FFB06BD4A7EF72E7F835" authority="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin, 2018" authorityName="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin" authorityYear="2018" box="[482,715,1927,1954]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrotarsata" status="sp. nov." subGenus="Asiosphegina">
<emphasis id="B972EA991977FFB06BD4A7EF72E7F835" box="[482,715,1927,1954]" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">S. (A.) nigrotarsata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A24157E21977FFB068E3A7E0731EF835" box="[725,818,1927,1953]" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<emphasis id="B972EA991977FFB06947A7EF746CF835" box="[881,1088,1927,1954]" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">
<taxonomicName id="4C064D081977FFB06947A7EF7410F835" authorityName="Kertesz" authorityYear="1914" box="[881,1084,1927,1954]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orientalis" subGenus="Asiosphegina">S. (A.) orientalis</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Except for the characters mentioned in the key 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D081977FFB06BF4A7CB728AF851" authority="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin, 2018" authorityName="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin" authorityYear="2018" box="[450,678,1963,1990]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="granditarsis" status="sp. nov." subGenus="Asiosphegina">
<emphasis id="B972EA991977FFB06BF4A7CB728AF851" box="[450,678,1963,1990]" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">S. (A.) granditarsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A24157E21977FFB06899A7CC7320F851" box="[687,780,1963,1989]" pageId="87" pageNumber="88" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differs from the other mentioned species by having only very sparse pile posteriorly on male sternum IV. The male genitalia are similar to those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D081978FFBF6A8BA16C71ACFEB0" authorityName="Kertesz" authorityYear="1914" box="[189,384,266,293]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="88" pageNumber="181" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orientalis" subGenus="Asiosphegina">
<emphasis id="B972EA991978FFBF6A8BA16C70E0FEB1" box="[189,204,267,293]" italics="true" pageId="88" pageNumber="89">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B972EA991978FFBF6AEDA16D70DAFEB0" box="[219,246,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="88" pageNumber="89">(A</emphasis>
.
<emphasis id="B972EA991978FFBF6AC8A16D71ACFEB0" box="[254,384,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="88" pageNumber="89">) orientalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but the dorsal lobe of surstylus is not widened on the apical part and the ventral lobe is pointed, not obtuse. Moreover, the long seta-like pile on the cercus is much longer. See also under 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D081978FFBF6A8BA13671A9FEFE" authority="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin, 2018" authorityName="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin" authorityYear="2018" box="[189,389,336,363]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="88" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atrimanus" status="sp. nov." subGenus="Asiosphegina">
<emphasis id="B972EA991978FFBF6A8BA13671A9FEFE" box="[189,389,336,363]" italics="true" pageId="88" pageNumber="89">S. (A.) atrimanus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A24157E21978FFBF6BBBA13771CBFEFE" box="[397,487,336,362]" pageId="88" pageNumber="89" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
